  * Changed "lusdll" from .F. to .T.
  -> vxh[-demo].exe now uses vxhdll[-demo].dll and xhbdll.dll to run
+ IDE/vxh-exe.exe.xbp
  * This script builds vxh-exe.exe that runs without vxhdll.dll
    and xhbdll.dll. It still needs ace32.dll.
